29 when only romania was still untouched by reform that soviet 
bloc espionage had increased 
around the world our stations are reporting more aggressive 
action a more robust intelligence collection effort more efforts 
to recruit our embassy and intelligence personnel than we have seen 
in a long time webster said 
the stuff is changing so fast that people are working hard 
just to keep up with it said one source at supreme headquarters 
allied powers europe 
