with her boss william agee in 1982 the two wed although they 
both deny they were romantically involved during the time she was 
at bendix 
since she started the nurturing network almost four years ago 
she has helped some 800 middleclass single women have babies from 
unplanned pregnancies 
and as the nation marks mondays anniversary of roe vs wade 
