notoriety 
her organization has tried to stay away from the abortion issue 
even as idaho lawmakers debate whether to enact restrictive 
legislation in the wake of last years us supreme court decision 
giving states some limited additional authority 
the nurturing network is not a forum for me to push forward my 
position on abortion mrs agee said my mission is not a 
political one but a practical one 
